high_descs: Turn left and go to the breakfast nook in front.
Take the knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Cut the apple inside the refrigerator.
Place the knife on the shelf above the apple.
Take one piece of the apple.
Close the refrigerator and go to the microwave to the right.
Microwave the apple piece and take it out.
Move to the other side of the breakfast nook with the black stools.
Place the apple next to the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of apple on the nook counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the end of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Cut the apple in the fridge into 3 pieces.
Place the knife on the top shelf in the fridge.
Pick up a piece of apple and shut the fridge.
Step to the right and face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn left and cross the room, then turn left and cross the room, and then turn left to face the counter.
Place the apple piece on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat an apple piece and place it on the counter next to the two stools.

high_descs: Turn left, then go to the rounded corner of the counter in front of you.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife from the edge of the counter.
Turn left, then go to the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge and cut up the apple that is in the fridge, next to the egg.
Put the knife on the shelf above the apple.
Grab a chunk of the apple.
Go to the microwave that is to the right of the fridge.
Cook the apple chunk in the microwave.
Turn left and go to the door, left again to the wall at the end of the counter, then turn around so the counter is on your right.
Lob the apple chunk to land between the tomato and the mug on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on a kitchen counter.
